        "title": "fix(slack): truncate approval mrkdwn on a UTF-16 boundary",
        "body": "## Problem\n`truncateSlackMrkdwn` shortens Slack approval mrkdwn text with a raw UTF-16 `.slice()`. An emoji near the limit is cut into a lone surrogate.\n\n## Fix\nUse the shared `truncateUtf16Safe` helper so truncation stops on a whole code-point boundary.\n\n## Proof\nAdded a regression in `extensions/slack/src/approval-handler.runtime.test.ts` — fails before, passes after. Pure unit test.\n",
